See https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-9468

Run the same code twice: 
```java
public class HelloWorld {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello, world!");
    }
}
```
* `Ctrl + Alt + R` to run as Java for the first time
* `Ctrl + R` to run as Groovy for the second time
![Run Java Code](https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12996743/RunJavaCode.png)
